      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your words carry a heavy weight of grief, and it is understandable to feel overwhelmed when the world feels so devoid of meaning. Often, the desire to escape pain is a natural reaction to suffering, but the very act of choosing to stay can be a powerful way to begin healing. If you feel ready, speaking to a trusted friend or a professional about these feelings might offer a new perspective. Remember that while the darkness feels comforting now, there is still hope for a future where the light returns.",
